<darktable_style version="1.0"><info><name>filmic</name><description>Parameterized filmic v6 tone mapping (#97). Modern darktable tone-mapping module with explicit log-encoding control; ships parallel to sigmoid (which covers ~80% of the basic tone-mapping use case). 8 magnitude axes: --param grey_point_source=V (default 18.45%), --param black_point_source=V (default -8.0 EV), --param white_point_source=V (default 4.0 EV), --param output_power=V (default 4.0; output gamma), --param latitude=V (default 0.01; midtone width), --param contrast=V (default 1.0; midtone slope), --param saturation=V (default 0.0), --param balance=V (default 0.0; tilts midtone toward shadows/highlights). Curve modes (shadows/highlights), color science version, and other enums are pinned at darktable defaults — author distinct discrete entries if you need different modes.</description></info><style><plugin><num>0</num><module>6</module><operation>filmicrgb</operation><op_params>9a999341000000c10000804000000000000040400000c8420000c84200000000000000009a9993412fa6783c0000c842000080400ad7233c0000803f0000000000000000cdcc4c3e0300000004000000010000000000000001000000010000000000000000000000000000000200000000000000</op_params><enabled>1</enabled><blendop_params>gz11eJxjYIAACQYYOOHEgAZY0QWAgBGLGANDgz0Ej1Q+dcF/IADRAGpyHQU=</blendop_params><blendop_version>14</blendop_version><multi_priority>0</multi_priority><multi_name></multi_name><multi_name_hand_edited>0</multi_name_hand_edited></plugin></style></darktable_style>
